* Iron Raptor roared as she saw Zenyak look back and suddenly look surprised and frightened, she really didn't appreciate being blown half to scrap and she wanted him to know that!
As she saw him run she picked up speed and soon began to close on him, simply taking the hits that managed to strike her as he shot backwards blindly as he ran.
The charges from his gun were barely felt as she came up behind him, now close enough to merely look down at him as they both ran.
Realizing that if she went any faster she would step on him she then ran a bit to the side and came up beside him, simply stepping on him being much to kind a fate!
Iron Raptor then suddenly swung her upper body around and in front of Zenyak, her massive head striking towards his chest-plate while her tail circled around on the other side...completely forming a circle around the Predacon.
She crouched so that Zenyak wouldn't be able to simply run between her feet and then rested the end of her tail by her head, striking at the bot with her fangs but with lightning fast reflexes that one she struck she then pulled back and struck again in mere seconds!
If he was able to throw and grenade and then run like the little coward she thought he was then he would suffer the strikes of an enraged woman!*
